   <head>Aduertisement of the Printer.</head>
   <p>THis REPLY, Good Rea<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>der, vvas indeed long since fi<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>nished by
the Author: but by reason of some impediment, it could not be
commodiously transported, so soone as he vvished, and desired it
